<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.15;
            font-size: 9.5px;
        }
        .page-container {
            padding: 0.2in 0.3in;
            min-height: 10.8in;
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
        .header-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f27022;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .logo-box {
            width: 100px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .ref-info {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 8.5px;
            color: #444;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .document-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 2px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .section-accent {
            border-left: 3px solid #f27022;
            padding-left: 8px;
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 10.5px;
            color: #f27022;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 5px 0 2px 0;
        }
        .content-body {
            font-size: 9.5px;
            text-align: justify;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .recipient-block {
            font-size: 9.5px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
        }
        .clause-item {
            margin-bottom: 0.5px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .clause-num {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .clause-text {
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .signature-wrapper {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .sig-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1.5px solid #000;
            width: 160px;
            padding-top: 3px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .sig-space {
            height: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0.15in;
            left: 0.3in;
            right: 0.3in;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 7.5px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 4px;
            color: #666;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0.5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== PAGE 1 ===== -->
<div class="page-container">
    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="logo-box"><img src="<%= logo %>" class="logo"></td>
            <td class="ref-info">
                Ref No: <%= offerId %><br>
                Date: <%= currentDate %>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="content-body">
        <div class="recipient-block">
            To,<br>
            <strong><%= employeeName %></strong><br>
            S/O Mr. <%= fathersName %><br>
            <%= address %><br>
            <%= phone %><br>
            <%= email %>
        </div>

        <div class="document-title">Appointment Letter</div>

        <div class="section-accent">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Subject: Appointment for the post of <%= position %></strong></p>
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong><%= employeeName.split(' ')[0] %></strong>,</p>
        <p>We are pleased to offer you the position of <span class="highlight"><%= position %></span> with <span class="highlight">VIRAL ADS MEDIA</span> on the following terms and conditions:</p>

        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">1.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Commencement:</span> Your employment will be effective as of <span class="highlight"><%= formattedJoiningDate %></span>.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">2.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Job title:</span> Your job title will be <span class="highlight"><%= position %></span>.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">3.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Salary:</span> Rs. <span class="highlight"><%= formattedSalary %>/- Per Month</span>.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">4.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Place of posting:</span> Rohini, Delhi.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">5.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Nature of duties:</span> You will perform duties as inherent in your post and additional duties as assigned.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-title">Office Hours Rules & Regulations</div>

        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">1.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Office Timings:</span> 9:30 AM to 6:30 PM. 10 min grace allowed twice a month.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">2.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Attendance:</span> 3 late marks = half-day. Biometric mandatory.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">3.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Leave Policy:</span> Pre-approval required. Emergency: inform before 9 AM.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">4.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Sandwich Leave:</span> Leave on both sides of weekend = all days counted as leave.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">5.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Early Leave:</span> Beyond 2 hours without approval = half-day.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">6.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Work Discipline:</span> No personal work, maintain decorum.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">7.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Rule Violation:</span> Verbal warning first, written warning next, termination for continued disregard.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">8.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Company Property:</span> Maintain and return all property before leaving.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">9.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Borrowing/Gifts:</span> No borrowing or accepting gifts from clients.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Viral Ads Media - Registered Office | B-27, Budh Vihar Phase 1, New Delhi-86 | Tel-9354491934
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== PAGE 2 ===== -->
<div class="page-break"></div>
<div class="page-container">
    <div class="content-body">
        <div class="section-title">Termination</div>

        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">10.1</div>
            <div class="clause-text">You may terminate by giving <span class="highlight">30 Days</span> prior notice.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">10.2</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Company may terminate summarily for misconduct or negligence.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">10.3</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Return all property, documents, and Confidential Information on termination.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-title">Confidential Information</div>

        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">11.1</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Devote full time to Company. No other business without permission.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">11.2</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Maintain confidentiality of all Company records and information.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">11.3</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Do not remove Confidential Information from office.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">11.4</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Confidentiality obligation survives termination.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">11.5</div>
            <div class="clause-text">Breach of confidentiality = summary dismissal.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-title">Notice Period</div>

        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">12.</div>
            <div class="clause-text">30 days notice period. Salary disbursed within 45 days of last working day.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">13.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Handover:</span> Hand over all files and assets properly.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">14.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Company Policy:</span> Company may alter policies at its discretion.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">15.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Governing Law:</span> Subject to Indian laws, jurisdiction Delhi High Court.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clause-item">
            <div class="clause-num">16.</div>
            <div class="clause-text"><span class="highlight">Acceptance:</span> Sign and return duplicate copy.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-wrapper">
            <p>We welcome you, and look forward to working with you.</p>
            <table class="sig-table">
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 50%; vertical-align: top;">
                        <p>Yours Sincerely,<br>For <strong>Viral Ads Media</strong></p>
                        <div class="sig-space"></div>
                        <div class="sig-line">Authorized Signatory</div>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 50%; text-align: right; vertical-align: top;">
                        <p>Accepted & Agreed</p>
                        <div class="sig-space"></div>
                        <div class="sig-line" style="margin-left: auto;">Employee Signature</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Viral Ads Media - Registered Office | B-27, Budh Vihar Phase 1, New Delhi-86 | Tel-9354491934
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>